title: Oscars Daddy - The ultimate crack finder
description:
Oscar&#039;s Daddy 2.0 

This application is very small but very useful. Oscar&#039;s Daddy is named after Oscar, the oldschool crack/keygen database. Oscar&#039;s Daddy was written by me to search and download keygens and cracks from a very large online database. 

The bonus is that you can get your cracks without fear of browser infection. 

Required .NET Framework 2.0 

For more information, screen shot and updates should there be any see http://onlythebest.codinghut.com/oscars-daddy/
